{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-jsx","path":"/blog/ukuleleLearningApp/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2>The problem</h2>\n<p>I wanted to help people who don’t have time to practice and learn the ukulele every day because I have a ukulele, and I found it <strong>hard to keep learning and practising the ukulele</strong>. According to the survey I did for people who are interested in ukulele or ukulele learners (around 20), this is the most common pain point they have.</p>\n<h2>The solution</h2>\n<p>I designed a ukulele learning app that will motivate people to play the ukulele every day. It <strong>minimizes the time that people need to spend on the ukulele while still making progress</strong> and has a <strong>virtual pet</strong> to keep them entering the app every day.</p>\n<h2>My role</h2>\n<p>I ran the entire project by myself by surveying to find out people’s needs and made the persona according to the needs and pain points I found. I also did the customer journey map, paper prototyping, low fidelity prototype and high fidelity prototype, and conducted the usability test.</p>\n<h2>Empathise with users</h2>\n<p>To empathise with users and find out their needs I did <strong>surveys from people who are interested in Ukulele or have experience with it</strong>. Surveying is one of the quickest and easiest ways to gather information in a short amount of time. Plus remaining COVID safe. I sent out the surveys on social media and in the end, 21 people responded. After summarising the results, here’s the persona I created based on the top three needs and pain points:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/31c49dfe7d59e9ebcc7b60552bb406f5/ba381/persona.webp 200w,\n/static/31c49dfe7d59e9ebcc7b60552bb406f5/7f61c/persona.webp 400w,\n/static/31c49dfe7d59e9ebcc7b60552bb406f5/d00b9/persona.webp 800w,\n/static/31c49dfe7d59e9ebcc7b60552bb406f5/92f8c/persona.webp 1200w,\n/static/31c49dfe7d59e9ebcc7b60552bb406f5/fad48/persona.webp 1600w,\n/static/31c49dfe7d59e9ebcc7b60552bb406f5/95d12/persona.webp 2661w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/31c49dfe7d59e9ebcc7b60552bb406f5/e07e9/persona.jpg 200w,\n/static/31c49dfe7d59e9ebcc7b60552bb406f5/066f9/persona.jpg 400w,\n/static/31c49dfe7d59e9ebcc7b60552bb406f5/4b190/persona.jpg 800w,\n/static/31c49dfe7d59e9ebcc7b60552bb406f5/e5166/persona.jpg 1200w,\n/static/31c49dfe7d59e9ebcc7b60552bb406f5/b17f8/persona.jpg 1600w,\n/static/31c49dfe7d59e9ebcc7b60552bb406f5/948ce/persona.jpg 2661w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/31c49dfe7d59e9ebcc7b60552bb406f5/4b190/persona.jpg\"\n            alt=\"User Persona\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n<em>User Persona</em></p>\n<h2>Ideate solutions</h2>\n<p>I did some research on existing Ukulele learning apps, such as Yousician. I adapted the <strong>gamified song challenge concept</strong> to make the practising experience more fun for the users. As illustrated in the final design section. I used the <a href=\"https://www.interaction-design.org/literature/article/learn-how-to-use-the-best-ideation-methods-scamper#:~:text=SCAMPER%20is%20an%20acronym%20formed,helps%20you%20explore%20new%20possibilities.\">SCAMPER</a> method to ideate. I also used the persona to produce an <a href=\"https://jmspool.medium.com/the-3-steps-for-creating-an-experience-vision-35f9d6ce378b\">experience vision</a>, which acts as a picture of what users' experience of using the design will be like.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/aa4eff59aed4af0fa04d3922545340cb/ba381/customerJourneyMap.webp 200w,\n/static/aa4eff59aed4af0fa04d3922545340cb/7f61c/customerJourneyMap.webp 400w,\n/static/aa4eff59aed4af0fa04d3922545340cb/d00b9/customerJourneyMap.webp 800w,\n/static/aa4eff59aed4af0fa04d3922545340cb/92f8c/customerJourneyMap.webp 1200w,\n/static/aa4eff59aed4af0fa04d3922545340cb/fad48/customerJourneyMap.webp 1600w,\n/static/aa4eff59aed4af0fa04d3922545340cb/92a1a/customerJourneyMap.webp 1607w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/aa4eff59aed4af0fa04d3922545340cb/e07e9/customerJourneyMap.jpg 200w,\n/static/aa4eff59aed4af0fa04d3922545340cb/066f9/customerJourneyMap.jpg 400w,\n/static/aa4eff59aed4af0fa04d3922545340cb/4b190/customerJourneyMap.jpg 800w,\n/static/aa4eff59aed4af0fa04d3922545340cb/e5166/customerJourneyMap.jpg 1200w,\n/static/aa4eff59aed4af0fa04d3922545340cb/b17f8/customerJourneyMap.jpg 1600w,\n/static/aa4eff59aed4af0fa04d3922545340cb/81abe/customerJourneyMap.jpg 1607w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/aa4eff59aed4af0fa04d3922545340cb/4b190/customerJourneyMap.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Customer Journey Map\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n<em>Customer Journey Map</em></p>\n<h2>Sketching &#x26; Wireframing</h2>\n<p>I started the design process by <strong>sketching on paper</strong>. I jotted down my very initial thoughts of what the <strong>main functions</strong> of this app should look like and what elements it should have.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 103%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/376f13fd78effab59e2ccc582cfe172b/ba381/PaperPrototype.webp 200w,\n/static/376f13fd78effab59e2ccc582cfe172b/7f61c/PaperPrototype.webp 400w,\n/static/376f13fd78effab59e2ccc582cfe172b/d00b9/PaperPrototype.webp 800w,\n/static/376f13fd78effab59e2ccc582cfe172b/92f8c/PaperPrototype.webp 1200w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/376f13fd78effab59e2ccc582cfe172b/e07e9/PaperPrototype.jpg 200w,\n/static/376f13fd78effab59e2ccc582cfe172b/066f9/PaperPrototype.jpg 400w,\n/static/376f13fd78effab59e2ccc582cfe172b/4b190/PaperPrototype.jpg 800w,\n/static/376f13fd78effab59e2ccc582cfe172b/e5166/PaperPrototype.jpg 1200w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/376f13fd78effab59e2ccc582cfe172b/4b190/PaperPrototype.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Customer Journey Map\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n<em>Paper Prototype</em></p>\n<h2>Testing my design</h2>\n<p>I did two runs of <strong>user evaluation</strong> with 5 people each run using the low-fidelity prototype shown in Figure 1. I used the <strong>think-aloud</strong> method to ask them to perform a few tasks and asked them to fill out a <strong>survey</strong> afterwards. I chose think-aloud method is because it's a very efficient way to know users' thoughts while they perform the tasks. Their feedback after the first user evaluation is summarised in Figures 2 and 3. And my changed design is shown in Figures 4 and 5.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 37.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/27af47cb34fec218d4d0a3dd00f54ffb/ba381/low-fiprototype.webp 200w,\n/static/27af47cb34fec218d4d0a3dd00f54ffb/7f61c/low-fiprototype.webp 400w,\n/static/27af47cb34fec218d4d0a3dd00f54ffb/d00b9/low-fiprototype.webp 800w,\n/static/27af47cb34fec218d4d0a3dd00f54ffb/92f8c/low-fiprototype.webp 1200w,\n/static/27af47cb34fec218d4d0a3dd00f54ffb/fad48/low-fiprototype.webp 1600w,\n/static/27af47cb34fec218d4d0a3dd00f54ffb/053bd/low-fiprototype.webp 2204w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/27af47cb34fec218d4d0a3dd00f54ffb/e07e9/low-fiprototype.jpg 200w,\n/static/27af47cb34fec218d4d0a3dd00f54ffb/066f9/low-fiprototype.jpg 400w,\n/static/27af47cb34fec218d4d0a3dd00f54ffb/4b190/low-fiprototype.jpg 800w,\n/static/27af47cb34fec218d4d0a3dd00f54ffb/e5166/low-fiprototype.jpg 1200w,\n/static/27af47cb34fec218d4d0a3dd00f54ffb/b17f8/low-fiprototype.jpg 1600w,\n/static/27af47cb34fec218d4d0a3dd00f54ffb/c337d/low-fiprototype.jpg 2204w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/27af47cb34fec218d4d0a3dd00f54ffb/4b190/low-fiprototype.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Figure 1, First Design\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n<em>Low-fi Prototype</em></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 16.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/ef6a9d164026bb2ec37aa4803795d728/ba381/1strunproblem1.webp 200w,\n/static/ef6a9d164026bb2ec37aa4803795d728/7f61c/1strunproblem1.webp 400w,\n/static/ef6a9d164026bb2ec37aa4803795d728/d00b9/1strunproblem1.webp 800w,\n/static/ef6a9d164026bb2ec37aa4803795d728/92f8c/1strunproblem1.webp 1200w,\n/static/ef6a9d164026bb2ec37aa4803795d728/fad48/1strunproblem1.webp 1600w,\n/static/ef6a9d164026bb2ec37aa4803795d728/21228/1strunproblem1.webp 1732w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/ef6a9d164026bb2ec37aa4803795d728/e07e9/1strunproblem1.jpg 200w,\n/static/ef6a9d164026bb2ec37aa4803795d728/066f9/1strunproblem1.jpg 400w,\n/static/ef6a9d164026bb2ec37aa4803795d728/4b190/1strunproblem1.jpg 800w,\n/static/ef6a9d164026bb2ec37aa4803795d728/e5166/1strunproblem1.jpg 1200w,\n/static/ef6a9d164026bb2ec37aa4803795d728/b17f8/1strunproblem1.jpg 1600w,\n/static/ef6a9d164026bb2ec37aa4803795d728/ce2f1/1strunproblem1.jpg 1732w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/ef6a9d164026bb2ec37aa4803795d728/4b190/1strunproblem1.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Figure 2, Problems raised after first user evaluation\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n<em>Figure 2, Problems raised after first user evaluation</em></p>\n<h4>Adjusted design:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Added names under icons</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 19.499999999999996%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/a4f0486e0fe1bba95d02adc200911f4d/ba381/1strunproblem2.webp 200w,\n/static/a4f0486e0fe1bba95d02adc200911f4d/7f61c/1strunproblem2.webp 400w,\n/static/a4f0486e0fe1bba95d02adc200911f4d/d00b9/1strunproblem2.webp 800w,\n/static/a4f0486e0fe1bba95d02adc200911f4d/92f8c/1strunproblem2.webp 1200w,\n/static/a4f0486e0fe1bba95d02adc200911f4d/fad48/1strunproblem2.webp 1600w,\n/static/a4f0486e0fe1bba95d02adc200911f4d/0eeae/1strunproblem2.webp 1736w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/a4f0486e0fe1bba95d02adc200911f4d/e07e9/1strunproblem2.jpg 200w,\n/static/a4f0486e0fe1bba95d02adc200911f4d/066f9/1strunproblem2.jpg 400w,\n/static/a4f0486e0fe1bba95d02adc200911f4d/4b190/1strunproblem2.jpg 800w,\n/static/a4f0486e0fe1bba95d02adc200911f4d/e5166/1strunproblem2.jpg 1200w,\n/static/a4f0486e0fe1bba95d02adc200911f4d/b17f8/1strunproblem2.jpg 1600w,\n/static/a4f0486e0fe1bba95d02adc200911f4d/91606/1strunproblem2.jpg 1736w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/a4f0486e0fe1bba95d02adc200911f4d/4b190/1strunproblem2.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Figure 3, Things to add suggested by the participants from the first user evaluation\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n<em>Figure 3, Things to add suggested by the participants from the first user evaluation</em></p>\n<h4>Adjusted design:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Added coins indicator</strong> indicating how many coins users have (<em><strong>A symbol stating how many coins I have</strong></em>)</li>\n<li><strong>Added information of how many coins do each song give users</strong> (<em><strong>How many coins do each song give me</strong></em>)</li>\n<li><strong>Added options to choose the pet</strong> (<em><strong>Options to choose the pet</strong></em>)</li>\n<li><strong>Added information of each suggested-to-practice song</strong> (<em><strong>Information about the suggested songs, whether they are randomly picked or I learned them</strong></em>)</li>\n<li><strong>Added a tuner</strong> (<em><strong>A tuner</strong></em>)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 68.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/b3a367e78af169aad5e402abddc3f700/ba381/low-fiPrototypeImproved1.webp 200w,\n/static/b3a367e78af169aad5e402abddc3f700/7f61c/low-fiPrototypeImproved1.webp 400w,\n/static/b3a367e78af169aad5e402abddc3f700/d00b9/low-fiPrototypeImproved1.webp 800w,\n/static/b3a367e78af169aad5e402abddc3f700/92f8c/low-fiPrototypeImproved1.webp 1200w,\n/static/b3a367e78af169aad5e402abddc3f700/fad48/low-fiPrototypeImproved1.webp 1600w,\n/static/b3a367e78af169aad5e402abddc3f700/a8768/low-fiPrototypeImproved1.webp 1816w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/b3a367e78af169aad5e402abddc3f700/e07e9/low-fiPrototypeImproved1.jpg 200w,\n/static/b3a367e78af169aad5e402abddc3f700/066f9/low-fiPrototypeImproved1.jpg 400w,\n/static/b3a367e78af169aad5e402abddc3f700/4b190/low-fiPrototypeImproved1.jpg 800w,\n/static/b3a367e78af169aad5e402abddc3f700/e5166/low-fiPrototypeImproved1.jpg 1200w,\n/static/b3a367e78af169aad5e402abddc3f700/b17f8/low-fiPrototypeImproved1.jpg 1600w,\n/static/b3a367e78af169aad5e402abddc3f700/7319a/low-fiPrototypeImproved1.jpg 1816w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/b3a367e78af169aad5e402abddc3f700/4b190/low-fiPrototypeImproved1.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Figure 4, Improved Design after first user evaluation\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n<em>Figure 4, Improved Design after first user evaluation</em></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 69.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/023cca74af5110eb7b909311e0330a29/ba381/low-fiPrototypeImproved2.webp 200w,\n/static/023cca74af5110eb7b909311e0330a29/7f61c/low-fiPrototypeImproved2.webp 400w,\n/static/023cca74af5110eb7b909311e0330a29/d00b9/low-fiPrototypeImproved2.webp 800w,\n/static/023cca74af5110eb7b909311e0330a29/92f8c/low-fiPrototypeImproved2.webp 1200w,\n/static/023cca74af5110eb7b909311e0330a29/fad48/low-fiPrototypeImproved2.webp 1600w,\n/static/023cca74af5110eb7b909311e0330a29/921bf/low-fiPrototypeImproved2.webp 1766w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/023cca74af5110eb7b909311e0330a29/e07e9/low-fiPrototypeImproved2.jpg 200w,\n/static/023cca74af5110eb7b909311e0330a29/066f9/low-fiPrototypeImproved2.jpg 400w,\n/static/023cca74af5110eb7b909311e0330a29/4b190/low-fiPrototypeImproved2.jpg 800w,\n/static/023cca74af5110eb7b909311e0330a29/e5166/low-fiPrototypeImproved2.jpg 1200w,\n/static/023cca74af5110eb7b909311e0330a29/b17f8/low-fiPrototypeImproved2.jpg 1600w,\n/static/023cca74af5110eb7b909311e0330a29/e993b/low-fiPrototypeImproved2.jpg 1766w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/023cca74af5110eb7b909311e0330a29/4b190/low-fiPrototypeImproved2.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Figure 5, Improved Design after first user evaluation\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n<em>Figure 5, Improved Design after first user evaluation</em></p>\n<h2>Final results</h2>\n<p>After two runs of user evaluation, the suggested improvements are summarised in Figure 6 and 7. I changed the design accordingly. You can find the <strong>interaction design</strong> <a href=\"https://www.figma.com/proto/NtW8DKFZKehVt4BqWOJPAG/High-Fidelity-Prototype?node-id=334%3A488&#x26;scaling=scale-down&#x26;page-id=0%3A1&#x26;starting-point-node-id=334%3A488\">here</a>.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 21.999999999999996%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/c206567a217265f756f20194d751b673/ba381/2ndrunproblem1.webp 200w,\n/static/c206567a217265f756f20194d751b673/7f61c/2ndrunproblem1.webp 400w,\n/static/c206567a217265f756f20194d751b673/d00b9/2ndrunproblem1.webp 800w,\n/static/c206567a217265f756f20194d751b673/92f8c/2ndrunproblem1.webp 1200w,\n/static/c206567a217265f756f20194d751b673/fad48/2ndrunproblem1.webp 1600w,\n/static/c206567a217265f756f20194d751b673/6bc2d/2ndrunproblem1.webp 1734w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/c206567a217265f756f20194d751b673/e07e9/2ndrunproblem1.jpg 200w,\n/static/c206567a217265f756f20194d751b673/066f9/2ndrunproblem1.jpg 400w,\n/static/c206567a217265f756f20194d751b673/4b190/2ndrunproblem1.jpg 800w,\n/static/c206567a217265f756f20194d751b673/e5166/2ndrunproblem1.jpg 1200w,\n/static/c206567a217265f756f20194d751b673/b17f8/2ndrunproblem1.jpg 1600w,\n/static/c206567a217265f756f20194d751b673/d93ec/2ndrunproblem1.jpg 1734w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/c206567a217265f756f20194d751b673/4b190/2ndrunproblem1.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Figure 6, Problems raised after first user evaluation\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n<em>Figure 6, Problems raised after first user evaluation</em></p>\n<h4>Adjusted design:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Added feedback when clicking on a page</strong> by making the page icon darker and having shadows (<em><strong>Not sure which page I was on</strong></em>)</li>\n<li><strong>Renamed the tabs page to be Tabs</strong> (<em><strong>Not sure what Tabular means</strong></em>)</li>\n<li><strong>Removed check-in button</strong> because users might just check-in and don’t do any practice. Now if users want to earn coins they will have to either practice a song or learn a new lesson. (<em><strong>Not sure what the check-in is for exactly</strong></em>)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 15.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/a4f1b464d957aff2818a9d5e012e64ef/ba381/2ndrunproblem2.webp 200w,\n/static/a4f1b464d957aff2818a9d5e012e64ef/7f61c/2ndrunproblem2.webp 400w,\n/static/a4f1b464d957aff2818a9d5e012e64ef/d00b9/2ndrunproblem2.webp 800w,\n/static/a4f1b464d957aff2818a9d5e012e64ef/92f8c/2ndrunproblem2.webp 1200w,\n/static/a4f1b464d957aff2818a9d5e012e64ef/fad48/2ndrunproblem2.webp 1600w,\n/static/a4f1b464d957aff2818a9d5e012e64ef/d50a6/2ndrunproblem2.webp 1738w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/a4f1b464d957aff2818a9d5e012e64ef/e07e9/2ndrunproblem2.jpg 200w,\n/static/a4f1b464d957aff2818a9d5e012e64ef/066f9/2ndrunproblem2.jpg 400w,\n/static/a4f1b464d957aff2818a9d5e012e64ef/4b190/2ndrunproblem2.jpg 800w,\n/static/a4f1b464d957aff2818a9d5e012e64ef/e5166/2ndrunproblem2.jpg 1200w,\n/static/a4f1b464d957aff2818a9d5e012e64ef/b17f8/2ndrunproblem2.jpg 1600w,\n/static/a4f1b464d957aff2818a9d5e012e64ef/5f433/2ndrunproblem2.jpg 1738w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/a4f1b464d957aff2818a9d5e012e64ef/4b190/2ndrunproblem2.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Figure 6, Problems raised after first user evaluation\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n<em>Figure 7, Things to add suggested by the participants from the first user evaluation</em></p>\n<h4>Adjusted design:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Added a profile page</strong> which <strong>shows users’ statistics</strong> such as learning experience points (<em><strong>A statistics page to see my progress</strong></em>)</li>\n<li><strong>Added plus signs before coins</strong> to indicate how many coins can users <strong>gain</strong> when they practice a song or learn a new content (<em><strong>A better indication that the coins will increase when practicing a song</strong></em>)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 105.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/0c7b6296f7acda7460749dd28cffccb0/ba381/finalDesign.webp 200w,\n/static/0c7b6296f7acda7460749dd28cffccb0/7f61c/finalDesign.webp 400w,\n/static/0c7b6296f7acda7460749dd28cffccb0/d00b9/finalDesign.webp 800w,\n/static/0c7b6296f7acda7460749dd28cffccb0/92f8c/finalDesign.webp 1200w,\n/static/0c7b6296f7acda7460749dd28cffccb0/1bc7b/finalDesign.webp 1364w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/0c7b6296f7acda7460749dd28cffccb0/e07e9/finalDesign.jpg 200w,\n/static/0c7b6296f7acda7460749dd28cffccb0/066f9/finalDesign.jpg 400w,\n/static/0c7b6296f7acda7460749dd28cffccb0/4b190/finalDesign.jpg 800w,\n/static/0c7b6296f7acda7460749dd28cffccb0/e5166/finalDesign.jpg 1200w,\n/static/0c7b6296f7acda7460749dd28cffccb0/6fffd/finalDesign.jpg 1364w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/0c7b6296f7acda7460749dd28cffccb0/4b190/finalDesign.jpg\"\n            alt=\"The final design\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n<em>The final design</em></p>\n<h2>Self-reflection</h2>\n<p>This is my first user design case study. I’ve familiarised myself with the design process. I haven’t applied any colours to the design yet, which could be an extension project.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Mukulele - Ukulele learning app","date":"February 19, 2022"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"4508fd4d-9d86-54c5-ada5-e2823c21420c"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}